tbGpIaXvmxDnA">Trương Hựu Tân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/Th%C3%ADnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%95ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-%C4%91%C3%A0n-H%E1%BB%93-gi%C3%A0-ki%C3%AAm-k%C3%BD-ng%E1%BB%AF-l%E1%BB%99ng-Ph%C3%B2ng-c%E1%BA%A5p-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-CRZA-bLce80ph3wIk6SQIw">Thính Đổng Đại đàn Hồ già kiêm ký ngữ lộng Phòng cấp sự - 聽董大彈胡笳聲兼寄語弄房給事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-K%E1%BB%B3/author-YrFgVDhYiheqwKg7ob0-Ig">Lý Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-th%E1%BA%A5t-u%C3%BD-T%C3%B9ng-T%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C3%A0i-v%C3%A2n/poem-m0yvfGYx_0U9oac8ZcDLUg">Tống Vương thất uý Tùng Tư, đắc Dương Đài vân - 送王七尉松滋，得陽臺雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-H%E1%BA%A1o-Nhi%C3%AAn/author-ep8IiRc7UH2qX75S-LVnLw">Mạnh Hạo Nhiên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BB%AB-%C3%B4-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-vfipuQZl6Jf9EmjtZ8xYPA">Từ ô dạ đề - 慈烏夜啼</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
